{
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.title": "苇草",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.epithet": "深池的影子",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "你好，初次见面。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.0-0r.ancient": "愿你的火焰能烧尽罪恶。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.ancient": "你见过她了，那个和我长得一样的人。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.char": "没有……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.IRONCLAD.1-2r.ancient": "哎，你记不得了吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.SILENT.0-0r.ancient": "你好。你头上的是什么？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.SILENT.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.SILENT.0-1r.char": "……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.SILENT.1-0r.ancient": "你不会说话吗？哎，没关系。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.0-0r.ancient": "你好。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.0-1r.char": "你好！你是这一片的王？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.0-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.0-2r.next": "……我是。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.1-0r.char": "为什么你又帮助我，又要和我打架？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.1-1r.ancient": "那个和我长得很像的，是我的姐姐。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.REGENT.1-2r.ancient": "她是导致这里不正常的元凶。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.ancient": "紫色的火……不对……她复活的不是骷髅……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.0-1r.char": "你在说什么？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.0-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.0-2r.ancient": "有一个非常危险的家伙，她的手下也全是冒着紫火。\n 既然你不是，那请你去消灭它们。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.ancient": "又见面了，骷髅。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.char": "你见过建筑师吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.NECROBINDER.1-2r.ancient": "还没有，不过我听说他杀死了你的生命，并导致你变成这个样子。这样的人，我一定会和他一战的。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.ancient": "你好，我该怎么称呼你？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.0-1r.char": "<随机混乱的语句>",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.ancient": "我去联系一下可露希尔，她肯定有办法修好你……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.1-1r.char": "<开心的表情>",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.2-0r.ancient": "罗德岛那边遭遇了重大变故，可露希尔说她暂时来不了……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.2-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.DEFECT.2-1r.char": "<失落的表情>",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.ANY.0-0.ancient": "你好，小心前方的火焰。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_REED.talk.ANY.1-0r.ancient": "远方的友人，又见面了。",
    "以下是风笛对话": "----------------------------------------------------------",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.title": "风笛",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.epithet": "风暴突击队队员",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "你好！需要帮忙吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.0-0r.ancient": "你好！小心点，不要点着旁边的麦田哦！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.ancient": "又见面了！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.char": "杀戮……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.IRONCLAD.1-2r.ancient": "哎？只会重复这两个字吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.0-0.ancient": "你好！你戴着兜帽是不想让别人认出来吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.1-0r.ancient": "你好！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.1-1r.char": "……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.SILENT.1-2r.ancient": "哎？你为什么不说话？我们又不是第一次见了！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.0-0r.ancient": "你好！你是……贵族？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.0-1r.char": "当然！我可是未来的王！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.1-0r.ancient": "你见过一个紫色的骷髅吗？她为什么什么都记不起来？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.REGENT.1-1r.char": "因为……建筑师[red]杀死[/red]了他们。而被涅奥复活时，记忆会丢失。",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.ancient": "你好……哇！你是被[purple]紫火[/purple]影响了吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.0-1r.char": "你是说我身上的火焰？你认识那家伙？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.ancient": "你好！你知道怎么解决[purple]紫火[/purple]吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.char": "我只知道我要向建筑师复仇！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.NECROBINDER.1-2r.ancient": "坏了，怎么还丢失记忆了？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.ancient": "你好！哇，机器人！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.0-1r.char": "<随机混乱的语句>",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.ancient": "你好！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.1-1r.char": "<随机混乱的语句>",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.DEFECT.1-2r.ancient": "哎哎，我好像不会修机器人哎……\n它在说什么……",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.0-0r.char": "下午好！我这里有一批[gold]兰登佳酿[/gold]滞销了，能帮帮我吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.0-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.0-1r.ancient": "好啊！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.1-0r.char": "下午好！上次委托你的那一批\n[gold]兰登佳酿[/gold]，销量如何？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ARCHETTO_CHARACTER_ARCHETTO.1-1r.ancient": "目前我已经卖出了[blue]{Beer}[/blue]瓶啦！",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ANY.0-0.ancient": "你好！初次见面，想要帮忙吗？",
    "ARKNIGHTS_MAP_EVENT_BAGPIPE.talk.ANY.1-0r.ancient": "又见面了，要在草垛上躺躺吗？",
